## ðŸ”‘ KEY API ENDPOINTS (Bookmark These!)

### Auth
```
POST /api/auth/register/
{
  "username": "john",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "pass123",
  "accessibility_preference": "normal"
}

POST /api/auth/login/
{
  "username": "john",
  "password": "pass123"
}
Response: { access, refresh, user }
```

### Messages
```
GET /api/messages/conversations/
Authorization: Bearer <token>

GET /api/messages/with_user/?user_id=2
Authorization: Bearer <token>

POST /api/messages/
Authorization: Bearer <token>
{
  "sender_id": 1,
  "receiver_id": 2,
  "content": "Hello!"
}
```

