## ðŸŽ¨ ACCESSIBILITY CSS QUICK COPY

```css
/* Normal Mode */
.theme-normal {
  background: #fff;
  color: #000;
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* Large Text */
.theme-large-text {
  background: #fff;
  color: #000;
  font-size: 20px;
}

/* High Contrast */
.theme-high-contrast {
  background: #000;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* Color-blind Friendly */
.theme-colorblind {
  background: #fef5e7;
  color: #1a3a3a;
  font-size: 14px;
}
```

